<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The 'if (err) { return err; }' branch in lfs_fs_mkconsistent is unreachable because LFS_LOCK(cfg) is defined as ((void)cfg, 0), so err is always 0 and the conditional can never be true. The return inside the if can never be executed, violating MISRA C 2023 Rule 2.1.
</scenario>
